	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />For reliable ROM information, see the NesCartDB.<br /><!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777">http://bootgod.dyndns.org:7777</a><!-- m --><br /><br />If you can split roms yourself, you can verify the CRC32s.  There are also SHA1 hashes available.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


