		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Calculating a CRC is quite easy. The wikipedia article shows it step by step how to do it by hand; then, you realise that you can achieve the same thing with a kind of modified &quot;Galois&quot; LFSR that shifts your data in the LFSR and XOR it with your polynomial.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
